      "source": [
        "# Clustering Method Comparison — Mean-Pooled Embeddings\n",
        "\n",
        "Runs all four clustering methods from `cluster_alts.py` on the pre-computed\n",
        "`mean_pooled_embeddings.pkl` file and visualizes each result with t-SNE.\n",
        "\n",
        "Clustering Algorithms Used:\n",
        "1. Fuzzy K-Means\n",
        "2. Spectral Clustering\n",
        "3. DBSCAN\n",
        "4. GMM"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "6effdd7a",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "6effdd7a"
      },
      "source": [
